{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "第十三回「斗室风云」：绝美女子冷月仙子艾青深夜闯入莫氏兄弟藏身的茅舍，追问北斗七煞下落。神手战飞、七巧追魂那飞虹、吴鸣世三人各怀心思，试图脱身事外。莫北被艾青身法震慑，莫南试图交涉未果。双方对峙之际，莫氏兄弟发射北斗七星针暗算，银针却直奔昏迷中的裴珏。吴鸣世舍身扑救，艾青施展万流归宗心法，以摄金吸铁之术将二十一口银针尽数收入袖中。众人认出艾青身份，战飞与她寒暄，得知裴珏竟是众人盟主大哥。艾青对裴珏的伤势和奇遇深感惊讶，温柔擦拭其额上汗珠。正欲追问之际，追杀艾青多年的神秘高手突然现身，艾青惊惶逃离，神秘人穿室而过紧追不舍。众人惊魂未定，晨曦微露，斗室之中只余一片混乱与谜团。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "绝美女子",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "你是谁？可就是北斗七煞？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "text": "姑娘又是谁？与那'北斗七煞'既然素不相识，寻他二人，又有何贵干？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_nan",
      "speaker_name": "莫南",
      "listener": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "text": "兄弟便是莫南，不知道姑娘寻找于我，为着何事？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bei",
      "speaker_name": "莫北",
      "listener": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "text": "你这女子，我兄弟与你素不相识，你深更半夜地来找我干什么？要知道……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "text": "这位姑娘与莫氏双杰有何过节，不妨说出来大家听听，老夫战飞……",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "绝美女子",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "你是什么东西，也配管我的闲事。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "绝美女子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们统统给我出去。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "text": "在下如果如此一走，日后传言出去，江湖中不知内情之人，还道在下等怕了姑娘，这却有些不便，何况……哈哈，在下虽是无名小卒，这两位兄弟，却是武林中大大有名的人物，恐怕不是姑娘能够呼之即来，挥之即去的哩！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "speaker_name": "吴鸣世",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "只要战兄愿意出去，小可更无所谓了……那兄，你说可是？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "text": "这个自然只要战兄带头，我便立刻出去，神手战飞能够如此，我七巧追魂那飞虹更无关系了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "speaker_name": "吴鸣世",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "正是，正是。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bei",
      "speaker_name": "莫北",
      "listener": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "text": "战兄、那兄俱都不必出去，还是我兄弟出去的好，反正此地地方太小，身手也施展不开。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "绝美女子",
      "listener": "char_mo_bei",
      "text": "你若喜欢到外面去死，也未尝不可。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_nan",
      "speaker_name": "莫南",
      "listener": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "text": "姑娘与我等究竟有何仇恨，不妨先说出来，也许……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "绝美女子",
      "listener": "char_mo_nan",
      "text": "北斗七煞不是贪淫好色，就是穷凶极恶，我早就想除去你们这批祸害了。哼！你们怎配与我有什么仇恨。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bei",
      "speaker_name": "莫北",
      "listener": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "text": "你又是什么东西……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "text": "裴大先生伤势虽不轻，所幸只是外伤而已，在下虽不才，对治这肋骨之伤，还有三分把握，艾仙子只管放心好了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "冷月仙子",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "世事变化，真不是人们可以预料得到的，我初次见到他时，他还只是个到处受人欺凌的少年，想不到仅仅几个月的日子，他竟变成了你们这些成名人物的盟主大哥。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "冷月仙子",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "text": "你可不可以告诉我，这短短几个月里，他到底有着什么奇遇？这真是教人心里奇怪得很。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "冷月仙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们还没走呀？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "speaker_name": "吴鸣世",
      "listener": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "text": "阁下可是冷月仙子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "冷月仙子",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "真的是你，你怎么会在这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "冷月仙子",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "他受的是什么伤？怎么受的伤？他是你们的什么人？你为什么要拼死救他。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "冷月仙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "伤得怎么这样重，只怕连骨头都碎了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "冷月仙子",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "盟主大哥……裴大先生……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "text": "在下们不知道阁下就是艾仙子，却也不知道艾仙子竟是我兄弟的盟主大哥裴大先生的朋友，这真是大水冲了龙王庙……哈哈，真是该死，真是该死。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "text": "吴兄，你和裴大先生既属知交，可知道他究竟是何来历，怎的和这位女魔头亦是素识？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "text": "这只怕连吴少侠也不知道吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "森冷口音",
      "listener": "char_jue_mei_nv_zi",
      "text": "想不到吧，又让我找着你，其实你又何苦如此苦苦逃避，就算你逃到天涯海角，难道我还会找不到你。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "那兄，你可带着火折子，唉，近年来我的确老了，目力已非昔日可比，吴兄，你年纪尚轻，你可看清后来那人的身形吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    }
  ],
